# ExNVR

## Restart ExNVR

Livebook connection will close, and any unsaved changes will be lost.

```elixir
System.restart()
```

## Reboot the Pi

Livebook connection will close, and any unsaved changes will be lost.

```elixir
System.cmd("sudo", ["reboot"])
```

